desc: Wyoming's Finest Mule Deer 2020 Edition features legendary Wyoming Mule Deer bucks in 408 pages of color photographs and stories. From Archery to Rifle Hunts, mule deer hunters can turn the pages of this book for hours on end. Enjoy the success of Wyoming's Muley hunters, and read about some of the Living Legends!

layout.text: 2020 Edition is available now - over 400 pages of Wyoming's biggest bucks!
